title: Good Morning, Neighbor 11
overview: This time Jelka and Milka go to the apple plantation as seasonal workers. And our Čedo is burning with jealousy, he dreams of Jelka being touched by unknown men, caressing her while he suffers... Čedo persuades his neighbor Nedja to investigate whether their wives are loitering in the orchards or earning their bread honestly?! Going on a long trip with Čedo's Vokswagen is always a special adventure, full of breakdowns and problems with the police.
